title: St George: Dragonslayer (from DHP 30-33) (2013|Dgtl-1680|Empire)
description:
This is "Saint George: Dragonslayer", serialized in "Dark Horse Presents" issues 30 thru 33.

The classic archetypical tale (man slays beast - damn, now I spoiled the ending), set in an equally classic but unconventional setting, which, along with a more nuanced dramatis personae, gives it a flavour more akin to Greek myth than to Medieval folklore. Lots of potential, in my opinion.

By Fred van Lente (  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Van_Lente#Bibliography" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Van_Lente#Bibliography</a>   ).
